    "html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"utf-8\">\n<style>\n  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }\n  body { width: 1080px; height: 1350px; overflow: hidden; }\n  .card {\n    width: 1080px; height: 1350px;\n    background: linear-gradient(160deg, #0d1f33 0%, #122c47 100%);\n    font-family: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', serif;\n    color: #ffffff;\n    display: flex; flex-direction: column;\n    padding: 90px 84px 70px 84px;\n    position: relative;\n  }\n  .logo { width: 210px; margin-bottom: 64px; }\n  .kicker {\n    font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\n    font-size: 30px; letter-spacing: 7px; font-weight: bold;\n    color: #c5a55a; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 44px;\n  }\n  h1 {\n    font-size: 88px; line-height: 1.14; font-weight: normal;\n    margin-bottom: 54px;\n  }\n  h1 .gold { color: #c5a55a; }\n  .rule { width: 130px; height: 5px; background: #c5a55a; margin-bottom: 54px; }\n  .sub {\n    font-size: 40px; line-height: 1.45; color: #d8dee6;\n    margin-bottom: 40px;\n  }\n  .sub strong { color: #ffffff; font-weight: normal; }\n  .punch {\n    font-size: 44px; line-height: 1.4; color: #c5a55a;\n    font-style: italic;\n  }\n  .footer {\n    margin-top: auto;\n    border-top: 2px solid rgba(197,165,90,0.45);\n    padding-top: 34px;\n    font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\n    font-size: 27px; color: #b9c2cc; letter-spacing: 0.5px;\n  }\n</style>\n</head>\n<body>\n  <div class=\"card\">\n    <img class=\"logo\" src=\"../../assets/phr_logo_white.png\" alt=\"Prestige Heritage Realty\">\n    <div class=\"kicker\">Condo Financing</div>\n    <h1>In 13 days, financing a Florida condo <span class=\"gold\">gets harder.</span></h1>\n    <div class=\"rule\"></div>\n    <div class=\"sub\">New Fannie Mae and Freddie Mac condo loan rules take effect <strong>August 3.</strong></div>\n    <div class=\"punch\">The bank will not just approve you. It will approve your building.</div>\n    <div class=\"footer\">Roger Averbuj, Broker | Prestige Heritage Realty | (954) 663-8461</div>\n  </div>\n</body>\n</html>\n",
